<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Teraskill Academy</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2); color: #fff; overflow-x: hidden;}
    header {background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); padding: 40px 0; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);}
    header h1 {font-size: 3em; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 2px;}
    header p {font-size: 1.2em; margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.9;}
    section.hero {display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px;}
    section.hero img {width: 60%; border-radius: 20px; margin-top: 30px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);}
    section.about {background: #fff; color: #333; padding: 80px 20px; text-align: center;}
    section.about h2 {font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 20px;}
    section.about p {font-size: 1.1em; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; line-height: 1.6;}
    section.gallery {background: #222; padding: 60px 0;}
    section.gallery h2 {text-align: center; font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 40px;}
    .images {display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; padding: 0 20px;}
    .images img {width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; transition: transform 0.3s ease; box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);}
    .images img:hover {transform: scale(1.05);}
    footer {background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center;}
    footer h3 {font-size: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 10px;}
    footer p {font-size: 1.1em; margin: 5px 0;}
    footer a {color: #ffcc00; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Teraskill Academy</h1>
    <p>Empowering Learning Through Technology and Innovation</p>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h2>Learn. Build. Grow.</h2>
    <p>Join our hands-on training programs designed to make you industry-ready!</p>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737604893-d14cc237f11d" alt="Training Session">
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About Teraskill Academy</h2>
    <p>Teraskill Academy is a modern learning hub designed for developers, engineers, and technology enthusiasts. Our mission is to provide practical, project-based learning experiences that empower learners to master emerging technologies, from DevOps to AI, Cloud, and beyond.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="gallery">
    <h2>Our Learning Moments</h2>
    <div class="images">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c" alt="Workshop">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091012184-7b4c1b1f5f9d" alt="Coding Session">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085" alt="DevOps Tools">
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    <p><strong>Your Name:</strong> Ponnam Phani Krishna</p>
    <p><strong>Telegram:</strong> <a href="https://t.me/yourtelegramid" target="_blank">@yourtelegramid</a></p>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Teraskill Academy. All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
